summary: This MOD creates two new bodies templates (CalienteTopless and CalienteVanillaTopless) inside Bodyslide v1-2-0 and 1-3-0. The bodies will still have the vanilla undies but not the bra.
descriptionHtml:
Topless Preset for Bodyslide 
-----------------------------------

This MOD creates two new bodies templates (CalienteTopless and
CalienteVanillaTopless) available in Bodyslide . The bodies will still
have the vanilla undies but not the bra.

No existent file is altered.

Expand this compressed archieve into the folder where Bodyslide
is located and the two new presets will be available the next
time Bodylside is started.

---------------------------------------------------------------

The CBBE Body and Bodyslide tool can be downloaded from:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

---------------------------------------------------------------

Big thanks to Caliente. Without her help this little MOD wouldn\'t
exist. CBBE rocks!
